Update 5: "Completed text outputs, added mathematical operations" Kirsten on 11/18/25 9:14 p.m.
Update 6: "Completed menu navigation" Kirsten on 11/19/25 10:13 p.m.
Update 7: "Completed mathematical operations" Kirsten on 11/19/25 11:05 p.m.
